description: Introducing herself as "Liz", she is a transfer student to Shuuhou Seiha Private School. A thirteen-year old child prodigy of English descent, Liz is extremely wealthy herself, a remarkable kendo student and immediately treats Naeka as her rival. Liz takes every opportunity and resource available to humiliate Naeka. She takes on the persona of "Strawberry Mask" as a disguise, even though everyone can easily tell who she is.
name: Elizabeth K. Strawberryfield
